Package: optimization
Type: Package
Title: Numerical Optimization with Nelder-Mead and Simulated Annealing
Version: 1.0-1
Date: 2016-11-20
Author: Kai Husmann and Alexander Lange
Maintainer: Kai Husmann <khusman1@uni-goettingen.de>
Description: Provides more flexibility than the optim() function in R base by means of further input specifications and and is applicable to more complex and specific functions. Includes visualization tools for validation and check for convergence of the algorithms.
